title: Saturday Night Live Season 7 Complete
description:
SNL Season 7 (1981-1982)

After Dick Ebersol Saved Saturday Night Live From Cancellation. It Became A Good Season. And The Great Return Of The Show. Eddie Murphy And Joe Piscopo. Became The Funniest Comedy Duos Of This Season. That Helped SNL Went Back Up To The Charts.

In This Season You'll Get To See. How The Show Returned Back Up To Late Night.

NOTE:You Probabaly Know That In Season 7. Mel Brandt Is The Annoucer. 
Instead Of Don Pardo.


So Anyways. Please Enjoy Season 7 Of Saturday Night Live.
